I need to identify and extract the line item and values related to interest accrued but not yet received.

Looking at the balance sheet, I need to find the appropriate line item that represents accrued interest. In accounting, this is typically listed as "Interest Receivable" - which represents interest that has been earned but not yet collected.

In the balance sheet provided, I can see the line item "Interest Receivable" with:
- Initial amount: 0.00 on 2023-12-31
- End amount: 14887.89 on 2024-02-05

Therefore, the interest accrued but not yet received has an initial value of 0.00 and an end value of 14887.89.
